OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScotRail strikes suspended 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter new pay offer        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A series of strikes at ScotRail have   
OL,6, been suspended after unions received an
OL,7, improved pay offer.                    
OL,9,FThe RMT is to ballot its members on a  
OL,10,F5% rise plus an extra #750, which is   
OL,11,F#250 more than the previous offer.     
OL,13,FScotRail said it meant wages would rise
OL,14,Fby 7.5% for staff such as conductors   
OL,15,Fand ticket examiners, with an 8.5%     
OL,16,Fincrease for lower-paid workers.       
OL,18,FThe RMT had been planning a strike next
OL,19,FSaturday followed by regular strikes on
OL,20,FFridays and Saturdays up to Christmas. 
